{"tid":2196634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港高官愛英磚頭 陳肇始、邱騰華有份","createTime":"2020-09-10T05:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T05:40:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9f52fb40cfd4249b24add855169be47f005d0165","tid":2196634,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200910/Y7UGPTUGSRG5LPAV7MFAMPGQVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200910%2FY7UGPTUGSRG5LPAV7MFAMPGQVE%2F&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE4CLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=0911526d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200910%2FY7UGPTUGSRG5LPAV7MFAMPGQVE%2F&h=7a601f43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200910/Y7UGPTUGSRG5LPAV7MFAMPGQVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港高官愛英磚頭 陳肇始、邱騰華有份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cEfse5b9czc4OfE0opzA_BSrR2o=/1535x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D6MI6P26XBARTFREOSJQGS227U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcEfse5b9czc4OfE0opzA_BSrR2o%3D%2F1535x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD6MI6P26XBARTFREOSJQGS227U.jpg&h=55d9e51d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■食物及衞生局局長陳肇始<br />\n<br />\n英國是港人海外投資熱門地之一，本港高官也有在該國買「磚頭」。據行政會議成員個人利益登記冊，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始與其親妹，於倫敦及格域（Gatwick）共擁有三個物業，全數作出租用途。商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華及其配偶，擁有三個位於倫敦的出租物業；而邱騰華申報的是「與家人聯名持有（jointly owned with family）」，從字眼上看，應是以個人而非公司名義持有物業。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：英披露外資持物業名單 維港2.4億買豪宅  周凱旋倫敦「私竇」曝光<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聶德權夫婦持出租物業<br />\n<br />\n除了陳肇始及邱騰華，公務員事務局局長聶德權與配偶，也共同持有一個英國伊斯靈頓（Islington）的出租物業。<br />\n<br />\n英國樓資深物業投資者James表示，第一次購買英國樓，通常會以個人名義購買，因首置可享免稅優惠，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在英國持有出租物業的公司，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產項目總監羅顯桂表示，。。。。"},{"pid":"43658a274c8930985e0bef5a7de5a194d4924e9b","tid":2196634,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"正常人類都會將資產保存係安全既地方<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠如是, 美國領事館撤資如是<br />\n<br />\n係港豬先仲會買港樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全世界SMART MONEY 走緊, 佢地去入市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4954bb350bb7af24544a18d2d1d50077059e5b9","tid":2196634,"uid":152705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"43658a274c8930985e0bef5a7de5a194d4924e9b","tid":2196634,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"正常人類都會將資產保存係安全既地方<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠如是, 美國領事館撤資如是<br />\n<br />\n係港豬先仲會買港樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全世界SMART MONEY 走緊, 佢地去入市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"仲要鳩叫gogogo , 一係話你酸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}